params.textField:
Get the Menu: Start by politely asking the waiter, &quot;Can I *see* a menu, please?&quot;
Ask for Help: If you&#039;re unsure about a dish, you can always ask the waiter, &quot;What would you *recommend*?&quot;
Ready to Order? Once you&#039;ve chosen your dish, use a clear phrase like, &quot;I&#039;d like to *order* the [dish name], please.&quot;
Drinks: For drinks, you can keep it simple with, &quot;Can I have some *water*, please?&quot;.

Special Requests: Do you have *allergies* or dietary restrictions? Let the waiter know politely! Say something like, &quot;I&#039;m allergic to *peanuts*, can you recommend something else?&quot;
Sides: Feeling extra hungry? You can add a *side dish* with, &quot;May I have a side of fries, please?&quot;
Enjoy! Relax, enjoy your delicious *meal*, and don&#039;t hesitate to ask the waiter if you need anything else.
